JINJA2 is usually use when for ex
when u hake a website for a school/clg
when the user login the page, then the welcome page should show (welcome and the users name)

hers the JINJA2 can to make the dynamic webpages
we can do everything like app addding python values, applying loops, conditions can be applied all u can do inside HTML template.

JINJA2 is a template engine inside the flask, we can use this to display python variables inside HTML.

---

---

syntax:
1- python values:
{{ variables}}

{{ name }}

ex: welcome {{ name }} #here the name will we replaced by the given input

---

2- conditions
{% if %}....{% endif %}

ex: is_topper = True
{% if is_topper %}

<p>You are a Topper</p>

{% else %}

<p>You need to work hard</p>

{% endif %}
